sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant S as Service
    participant P as auth-api (:7011)
    participant R as Client Registry (SM)
    participant K as Keyset (active kid)

    S->>P: POST /v1/oauth/token grant_type=client_credentials
    P->>R: validate client_id + secret (constant-time)
    R-->>P: allowed scopes (fail-closed if empty)
    P->>K: sign RS256 — scope svc:CLIENT_ID, per-service aud, 1h
    K-->>P: signed JWT
    P-->>S: snake_case RFC 6749 response
    Note over S: cached via WithServiceAuth
